title: Unimproved Property for Camping or Stealth Living
posting_body: I have a nice little private lot on a hillside.
I’m interested in renting it out as a camp site temporarily or longer term.
Please email me your story/needs and let’s see if my property could be compatible.
Everything would need to be packed in and out of the property.
I bought this property because I really like the area and thought that my baby’s dad was going to be around to help build a house for the baby and me.
His plans changed and I would still like to keep the property.
I’m still pregnant right now about 7months and not able to work like normal (80+ hours a week)
so I’m going to be needing some help covering bills for the next few months.
This lot is pretty much only good for camping so if anyone is into camping or stealth living this might be the perfect place for you.
Please contact me if you are interested and we can figure something out.
I put $500 tentatively as a monthly rate assuming it would be used several times a month.
So if you are looking for cheaper and just an overnight or two here and there please let me know and we could come up with a fair nightly rate.
This is a link with some photos.
